## TEMPLATE — DO NOT EDIT directly.
##
## This empty placeholder is committed so docker-compose.yml has something
## to bind-mount even on fresh checkout (Docker would otherwise create an
## empty DIRECTORY, breaking Mosquitto).
##
## setup.sh REPLACES this file with `mosquitto_passwd`-generated hashes.
##
## To generate manually:
##   docker run --rm -v $PWD/config:/mosquitto/config eclipse-mosquitto:2.0 \
##     mosquitto_passwd -c -b /mosquitto/config/passwd frigate YOUR_PASSWORD
